    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Granted Powers:</strong> You are infused with the glory of the divine, and are a true foe of the undead. In addition, when you channel positive energy to harm undead creatures, the save DC to halve the damage is increased by 2.</p>\n<p><strong>Domain Spells:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>1st—@Compendium[pf1.spells.y2uhoqr4itdbw5g4]{Shield Of Faith}</li>\n<li>2nd—@Compendium[pf1.spells.hl9l92qfalq6c55z]{Bless Weapon}</li>\n<li>3rd—@Compendium[pf1.spells.dnet1tyxbsnwailm]{Searing Light}</li>\n<li>4th—@Compendium[pf1.spells.erndkoe44rgj0lob]{Holy Smite}</li>\n<li>5th—@Compendium[pf1.spells.6ax0ythzw8n4bta8]{Righteous Might}</li>\n<li>6th—@Compendium[pf1.spells.lllhr9py6w44cxjm]{Undeath to Death}</li>\n<li>7th—@Compendium[pf1.spells.osi62mwn6rpkwlm6]{Holy Sword}</li>\n<li>8th—@Compendium[pf1.spells.n0vm6or4nwaylpfa]{Holy Aura}</li>\n<li>9th—@Compendium[pf1.spells.ursm11405zobemi3]{Gate}</li>\n</ul>",
